        "text": "Verification",
      },
      "type": "Heading",
    },
    "link-10": {
      "children": [],
      "props": {
        "href": "https://example.com/pr/412",
        "label": "Open PR #412",
      },
      "type": "Link",
    },
    "markdown-1": {
      "children": [],
      "props": {
        "content": "The TTL was **30 seconds** while the upstream sync runs every **5 minutes**, so the cache was cold for most of every window. The fix lives in \`src/api/cache.ts\`.",
      },
      "type": "Markdown",
    },
    "markdown-3": {
      "children": [],
      "props": {
        "content": 
"- The first request after a sync repopulates the key.
- Every request 30s later misses again and hits Postgres.
- Postgres sees ~8x the read volume it should."
,
      },
      "type": "Markdown",
    },
    "root": {
      "children": [
        "heading-0",
        "markdown-1",
        "heading-2",
